    "title": "Uvumulivu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "uvumulivu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wakati Yesu alipokaribia kuteseka na kufa, aliwaambia wafuasi wake kwamba wao pia wangepitia changamoto kubwa (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:9\">Mathayo 24:9</a>). Alisisitiza umuhimu wa uvumilivu: “Yule anayevumilia hadi mwisho ataokolewa” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:13\">Mathayo 24:13</a>). Maandiko mengi ya Agano Jipya yaliandikwa kwa ajili ya Wakristo waliokuwa wakiteseka kwa ajili ya imani yao katika Kristo (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2 Wathesalonike 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:19\">1 Petro 4:12–19</a>). Wakristo hawa walihitaji kutiwa moyo ili kuvumilia changamoto huku wakibaki waaminifu kwa Kristo na kushiriki imani yao na wengine (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:5\">2 Timotheo 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1\">1 Petro 4:1</a>). Kupitia uvumilivu, Wakristo hukua katika tabia na kukuza ukomavu wa kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">Warumi 5:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">Yakobo 1:2–4</a>).</p><p>Kitabu cha Waebrania kilizungumza kuhusu Wakristo waliokumbana na changamoto nyingi. Watu waliwasumbua, wakachukua mali zao, na kuwafunga gerezani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:32-Heb10:34\">Waebrania 10:32–34</a>).</p><p>Wakati wa kuandika, walikuwa na masuala yanayofanana. Walihitaji &quot;kushikilia kwa uthabiti&quot; imani zao bila kuyumba (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:14\">4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">10:23</a>). Walipaswa kuvumilia huku wakisubiri ahadi za Mungu zitimie (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:36\">10:36</a>). Kama wakimbiaji katika mbio, walihitaji &quot;kukimbia kwa uvumilivu mbio zilizowekwa mbele yao&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">12:1</a>). Kama watoto wa kweli wa Baba mwenye upendo, walipaswa kukubali nidhamu ya Bwana ili wakue katika utakatifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:13\">12:5–13</a>).</p><p>Mifano bora ya uvumilivu katika Maandiko, kama vile Ayubu na manabii, inaweza kuwahamasisha Wakristo wote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:35-Heb11:40\">Waebrania 11:35–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:10-Jas5:11\">Yakobo 5:10–11</a>). Kristo, mfano wetu mkuu wa uvumilivu, &quot;alivumilia msalaba,&quot; kwa sababu ya &quot;furaha iliyowekwa mbele Yake&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:3\">12:1–3</a>). Tumaini hili la siku zijazo linatuhamasisha kuvumilia.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">Warumi 5:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:12\">1 Wakorintho 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2 Wathesalonike 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">Waebrania 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:10\">Waebrania 12:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">Yakobo 1:2–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">Yakobo 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:20\">1 Petro 2:20</a></p>",
